just an installed group of people

62
00:03:53,609 --> 00:03:55,350
that you know in the industry right off the bat,

63
00:03:55,910 --> 00:03:57,291
the people that you work with in college.

64
00:03:58,011 --> 00:04:03,994
downsides, because these may not be downsides for you, but projects are really long-term.

65
