00:29:20,553 --> 00:29:22,654
But I needed to make sure that...

556
00:29:23,563 --> 00:29:24,524
I can limit everything.

557
00:29:24,544 --> 00:29:27,146
Because saying no is really, really hard,

558
00:29:27,766 --> 00:29:29,928
and sometimes you just have to let people down,

559
00:29:30,388 --> 00:29:32,570
which in a trust fall, maybe you don't want to do.

560
00:29:33,090 --> 00:29:36,613
But 95% of the time, all you're doing

561
00:29:36,653 --> 00:29:37,974
is setting acceptable boundaries

562
00:29:38,214 --> 00:29:40,776
and making sure that other people

563
00:29:41,757 --> 00:29:42,678
can take care of themselves.

564
00:29:43,218 --> 00:29:45,159
I like to think, what's the worst that can happen?

565
00:29:46,040 --> 00:29:48,842
Most of the time, people might get a little bit miffed,

566
00:29:48,882 --> 00:29:50,163
they might get a little bit angry at you,

567
00:29:50,944 --> 00:29:52,465
but the long-term repercussions aren't there.

568
00:29:53,556 --> 00:29:56,058
