570
00:29:59,259 --> 00:30:00,400
and you wanna make sure you understand

571
00:30:00,480 --> 00:30:02,541
why you are saying no to things when you do.

572
00:30:03,182 --> 00:30:04,883
You wanna make sure you own that decision

573
00:30:05,403 --> 00:30:07,484
because you can't let people reverse that

574
00:30:07,604 --> 00:30:08,425
and walk all over you.

575
00:30:09,165 --> 00:30:11,407
You also want to make sure that you know why.

576
00:30:11,828 --> 00:30:13,369
Is it because you don't want to do it?

577
00:30:13,769 --> 00:30:14,950
Is it because you're overloaded?

578
00:30:15,271 --> 00:30:16,872
Is it something you might want to revisit later?

579
00:30:17,653 --> 00:30:21,096
Understanding your own self is just very critical here.

580
00:30:22,077 --> 00:30:24,098
Because time is money, we only have a limited amount

581
00:30:24,118 --> 00:30:25,880
of time in our lives, and we need to use it

582
00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:26,961
to the best of our ability.

583
00:30:27,521 --> 00:30:29,863
You need to learn how to hand things off to other people

584
00:30:30,404 --> 00:30:32,886
and realize that you don't have to do everything yourself

585
00:30:32,966 --> 00:30:34,227
and you can't do everything yourself.

