746
00:38:13,411 --> 00:38:16,313
But again, at the end of the day, you're the one that lives with it.

747
00:38:17,354 --> 00:38:18,335
So trust yourself.

748
00:38:18,715 --> 00:38:20,096
You're the hero of your story.

749
00:38:20,156 --> 00:38:25,580
