00:43:15,574 --> 00:43:17,254
So if you get one thing out of this talk,

844
00:43:17,314 --> 00:43:20,976
I want it to be that investing in your peer relationships

845
00:43:21,036 --> 00:43:23,116
will have the biggest impact on your career

