00:45:04,118 --> 00:45:05,899
So let's go back to that thing about trust.

878
00:45:06,739 --> 00:45:09,820
So as your paths diverge, that trust remains.

879
00:45:10,240 --> 00:45:12,400
This is how team ups create new opportunities,

880
00:45:12,460 --> 00:45:13,261
that third point.

881
00:45:14,021 --> 00:45:17,022
So new opportunities come from past team ups.

882
00:45:17,342 --> 00:45:19,642
At senior levels, most of your new gigs

