00:45:19,682 --> 00:45:20,582
will happen this way.

884
00:45:21,143 --> 00:45:23,143
And this isn't nepotism, it's risk management.

885
00:45:23,203 --> 00:45:24,463
It's good hiring practice.

886
00:45:25,464 --> 00:45:26,984
Senior developers are expensive,

887
00:45:27,064 --> 00:45:29,705
