00:45:35,163 --> 00:45:37,564
that another person trusts that says,

890
00:45:37,584 --> 00:45:39,364
I would definitely work with this person again.

891
00:45:42,525 --> 00:45:44,606
So this might be how you break into the AAA space

892
00:45:47,227 --> 00:45:48,247
and join your dream team.

893
00:45:49,687 --> 00:45:51,988
Or it could be how you all quit your jobs,

