00:45:52,248 --> 00:45:54,269
you and your peers, to launch your own thing.

895
00:45:55,629 --> 00:45:58,170
The bottom line is that teaming up, investing in people,

896
00:45:59,238 --> 00:46:01,139
And leaving behind teammates who trust you

